  "text": "Traumatic Events Inventory. Thetraumatic events inventory (TEI) [CITATION_1] 65 assesses lifetime history of trauma exposure and isourprimarymeasureofbothchildabuse and non-child abuse trauma. The TEI assesses past experience and frequency of 13 separate types of traumatic events as well as feelings of terror, horror, and helplessness with such events.",
